OL,3,C100 MPs back Waspi letter urging
OL,4,CGovernment to 'reach the right
OL,5,Cdecision'
OL,7,FWaspi campaigners say they have
OL,8,Fgathered support from 100 MPs for a
OL,9,Fletter urging the Government to "reach
OL,10,Fthe right decision" for 1950s-born
OL,11,Fwomen.
OL,13,FThe letter urges Secretary of State
OL,14,Ffor Work and Pensions Pat McFadden to
OL,15,Fgive an update on plans by March 2 "at
OL,16,Fthe latest".
