OL,5,Cdecision'
OL,7,FIn November, Mr McFadden said his
OL,8,Fdepartment would review a previously-
OL,9,Fannounced policy not to compensate
OL,10,Fwomen born in the 1950s who were
OL,11,Faffected by increases in the pension
OL,12,Fage, for the way the changes were
OL,13,Fcommunicated.
OL,15,FIt came as court proceedings led to
OL,16,Fthe rediscovery a 2007 Department for
OL,17,FWork and Pensions (DWP) evaluation
OL,18,Fwhich had led to officials stopping
OL,19,Fsending automatic pension forecast
OL,20,Fletters out.
