OL,5,Cdecision'
OL,7,FHowever, Mr McFadden offered
OL,8,Fcampaigners no guarantees that the
OL,9,Freview would lead to compensation
OL,10,Fbeing awarded.
OL,12,FThose behind the campaign said the
OL,13,Fletter will be sent on Thursday.
OL,15,FAngela Madden, chairwoman of Women
OL,16,FAgainst State Pension Inequality
OL,17,F(Waspi), said: "It's high time that
OL,18,Fministers stopped stalling and started
OL,19,Fcompensating Waspi women."
