OL,7,FBut in December 2024, the Government
OL,8,Fsaid that, while it accepted the
OL,9,Fombudsman's finding of
OL,10,Fmaladministration and apologised for a
OL,11,Fdelay in writing to 1950s-born women,
OL,12,Fa blanket compensation scheme, which
OL,13,Fcould cost taxpayers up to #10.5
OL,14,Fbillion, could not be justified.
OL,16,FA DWP spokesperson said: "Last month
OL,17,Fwe committed to retake the decision
OL,18,Fand as set out, we will do so within
OL,19,Fthe three-month period.
